Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐龙曾统治地球...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dinosaurs ruled the planet 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(大卫爱登堡主持)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...超过一亿五千万年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for over 150 million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎在地球的每个角落 都可以找到它们的踪迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They occupied almost every corner of the globe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而它们的体型和大小各异\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and came in almost every shape and size imaginable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些恐龙确实非常独特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some were truly extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今 我们知道霸王龙是游泳健将\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We now know that T. rex was a powerful swimmer,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅猛龙则是长着羽毛的狡猾猎手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Velociraptors were cunning, feathered hunters,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些恐龙的行为相当怪异\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and that some dinosaurs had the most bizarre behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 几乎每天都有新的发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But new discoveries are being made almost every day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭示更多关于六千六百万年前 地球上生物的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that tell us more about life on this planet 66 million years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本季的《Prehistoric Planet》中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This time on Prehistoric Planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将展示全新的动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we reveal new animals...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和关于它们寻找伴侣的新发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and new insight into their quest to find a partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚养一个家庭所面临的挑战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the challenges faced by raising a family...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.49,0:01:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及它们间重量级的战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and their titanic battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带领您穿越时光 探访大自然最壮丽的那个时代\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Journey to a time when nature put on its greatest show.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽在《Prehistoric Planet 2》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Prehistoric Planet 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:02:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}荒地\N第二季第二集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:02:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}本WEB版外挂字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}风吹来的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  双语合并
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一亿年来 地球上最大的一片熔岩流所覆盖的区域\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the largest expanse of lava to flood the earth for 100 million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印度中部的德干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Deccan in central India,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个如同地狱般的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a hellish place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 这里并非你能想到的恐龙出没之地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and certainly not where you would expect to find dinosaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 巨大的恐龙 却冒着生命危险来到了这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yet, giants risk their lives traveling here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊希斯龙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isisaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且它们都是雌性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And all are females.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在德干 熔岩源源不断地涌动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lava has been flowing in the Deccan for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久而久之 有些地方 岩浆的厚度达到了1.6公里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that in places, it is a mile thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年春天 雌性伊希斯龙 都会离开安全的森林家园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every spring, females leave the safety of their forest home
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏上危险的旅程 进入这片荒地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to make a perilous journey into these badlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管它们可以在冷却硬化的熔岩上 选择一条安全路线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They can pick a safe route through cooled, hardened lava...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这里还充斥着其他危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but there are other dangers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了蒸汽外 火山喷口 还会喷出致命的二氧化碳和\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In addition to the steam, a deadly mixture of carbon dioxide and hydrogen sulfide
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硫化氢混合物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}spews from volcanic vents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黎明前的凉爽空气中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the cool pre-dawn air,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些沉重的气体会下沉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}these heavy gases sink
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形成一层几乎看不见的 令人窒息的毒气帷幕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to create a barely visible, suffocating blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅吸入几口就足以致命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a few lungfuls can kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 伊希斯龙异龙有一个关键的优势\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But isisaurs have one crucial advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们的长脖子可以让头部 保持在这片有毒气体之上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their long necks can keep their heads above this blanket of poisonous fumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在前方的某处 它们很难使头部远离有毒气体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But ahead lies a place where this will be hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们正进入一个低洼地带\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're entering a low-lying area
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的致命气体特别浓厚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where the deadly gases are particularly thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这些雌性伊希斯龙 已经感觉有些不对劲了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And for these females, something is already wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更糟糕的是 当太阳升起 温暖了空气后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And worse, as the sun rises and warms the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有毒气体会上升得更高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the gases swirl even higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长脖子已经不能保护这群恐龙了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long necks can no longer protect the herd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们必须迅速逃到更高的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They must escape to higher ground and quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:06:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然高地很陡峭 但在上面应该有更新鲜的空气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The climb is steep but should bring fresher air.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们终于得救了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Relief at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方是它们此次旅程的最终目的地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And ahead, their final destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个高耸入云的火山岛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A volcanic island in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屹立于这片险恶的荒地之上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}rising high above these treacherous badlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个巨大的火山口是一个破火山口 为它们提供了一个安全的集体筑巢地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The huge crater, a caldera, provides a safe communal nesting ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围环绕的层层有毒气体 有助于阻挡捕食者进入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The surrounding sea of poisonous gases helps to keep predators away...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时 内置的地热加热系统 使这里成为理想的孵化器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the inbuilt geothermal heating makes it an ideal incubator.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个恐龙妈妈都在温暖的沙地上 挖一个2米深的沟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Each mother digs a seven-foot trench in the warm sand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来放置超过20个像瓜那么大的蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to hold over 20 melon-sized eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些蛋在这个破火山口暂时很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The eggs are safe in the caldera for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这仅仅是它们故事的开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but this is just the beginning of their story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在几个月后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a few months,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:08:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成百上千的恐龙宝宝将孵化出来 面对这个荒凉的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}hundreds of tiny babies will hatch to face this desolate world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If any are to survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们需要周围条件恰到好处的变化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they'll need a perfectly timed change in conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在史前地球上的荒地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The badlands of the prehistoric planet
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连恐龙都受到了生与死的考验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}tests even dinosaurs to their limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片奇特的景观\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This strange landscape
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由侵蚀性的强风和巨大的古河流塑造而成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}carved by scouring winds and vast ancient rivers
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看似寸草不生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}might appear empty of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而在亚洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But here in Asia,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些峡谷的蜿蜒深处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}hidden in these narrow canyons...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏着一个新生的迅猛龙家族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is a new family of Velociraptors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些幼崽才几周大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The young are just a few weeks old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这贫瘠的环境中 它们似乎面临着未知的命运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It might seem that in such a barren place, they face an uncertain future.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们的生存取决于一个奇怪事件 发生在离它们家数公里外的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their survival relies on a strange event, not here, but miles from their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在炙热的沙漠对面 有一片被沙海环抱的森林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Across the baking desert lies a forest trapped in a sea of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,季节的变化为这片区域带来了稀有的水源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A change in the seasons brings rare water to this region.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大片的白杨树\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Huge stands of poplar trees
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒出营养丰富的叶子 标志着雨水的到来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}mark its arrival with a flush of nutritious leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会引来大量饥肠辘辘的动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A magnet that draws many hungry animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长颈的耐梅盖特龙 与蒙古泰坦巨龙一起前来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long necked nemegtosaurs are joined by Mongolian titanosaurs...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同行的还有体型小得多的倾头龙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and with them, much smaller Prenocephale.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在它们的旅程中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But one thing stands in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一片广袤的高原阻挡了去路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This immense plateau.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一抵达森林的途径 就是穿越这迷宫般的峡谷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the only way to reach the forest is through this maze of canyons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当这群恐龙进入峡谷时 它们变得紧张起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As they enter, the herd becomes nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是伏击的好地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a good place for an ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅猛龙正恭候在此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Velociraptors are waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它们无法战胜泰坦巨龙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But they can't possibly tackle a titanosaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伏击能否成功取决于其他潜行的猎手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Success will depend instead on other hunters on the prowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特暴龙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tarbosaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚洲版的霸王龙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Asia's version of Tyrannosaurus rex.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着掠食者的逼近 恐慌蔓延开来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As the predators approach, panic spreads.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有倾头龙能逃到更高的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only the Prenocephale can escape to higher ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅猛龙等待的正是这个时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this is what the Velociraptors have waited for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 它们终于可以发动致命的伏击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, the Velociraptors can finally spring their ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于得手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At last.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们齐心协力为整个家族 争取到了一顿美餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Working together, they have secured a meal for the whole family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特暴龙也成功捕获了猎物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The tarbosaurs have also had success.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于掠食者来说 这实际上是一个食物充足的时期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For predators, it's actually a time of plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于迅猛龙来说 现在是组建家庭的最佳时机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And for the Velociraptors, the perfect time to start a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有智慧且充满关爱的父母 能为孩子提供一个美好的开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Having clever, caring parents can give youngsters an excellent start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在亚洲的荒地上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And here in the badlands of Asia,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一群更敬业的恐龙父母\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there are few more dedicated dinosaur parents than these.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们就是正在筑巢的冠盗龙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A colony of nesting Corythoraptors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几天前 雌性冠盗龙 在这些圆形土丘上产下了蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A few days ago, females laid eggs on these circular mounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而孵蛋的重担则落在了雄性身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the job of brooding them falls to the males.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:15:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这并不容易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that is not easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴露在正午的阳光下 这些蛋很快就会被烤熟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Exposed to the midday sun, the eggs would soon cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是爸爸们用它们 宽大的尾巴和前臂上的羽毛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the fathers use their broad tail and forearm feathers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为鸟巢遮荫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to keep the nest shaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并付出沉重的代价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And pay a heavy price.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承受着长时间的高温\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enduring hour after hour in the searing heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于 在凉爽的夜晚 雄性冠盗龙可以离开去寻找食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At last, in the cool of the evening, the males can step away in search of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是群体孵化带来的好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is when nesting in a colony brings benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠盗龙爸爸们并没有同时离开 而是轮流去觅食\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Instead of all leaving at once, the Corythoraptors take turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 总有一个邻居在站岗 密切注意着可能的危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, there's always a neighbor keeping an eye out for danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 即使是邻里守望 也不能保证它们的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But even this neighborhood watch can't guarantee their safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一只雌性作明龙 迅猛龙的近亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A female Kuru kulla, a relative of Velociraptors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它饥肠辘辘 但提防着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is extremely hungry but wary
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠盗龙有力的喙和爪子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the Corythoraptors' powerful beaks and claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 它拥有一个关键优势\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But she has one key advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的夜视能力远胜于巢穴的主人们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her night vision is better than that of the owners of the nests.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果它悄无声息 就可以不被察觉地潜入冠盗龙群\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If she's quiet, she can sneak into the colony undetected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它谨慎地选定目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She picks her target carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is her chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它不是去攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But not to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个掠食者也是个小偷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This predator is also a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它会以最快的速度吃掉尽可能多的蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She will eat as many eggs as fast as she can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了 它被发现了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Time's up. She's been discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上最后一个蛋逃之夭夭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One last egg to take away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 这个小偷有机会 安静地享用偷来的蛋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She now has a chance to enjoy her stolen egg in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它并未独自享用战利品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But this thief shares her spoils.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它用呼噜声召唤自己的孩子们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With these purring sounds, she calls her young.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些幼崽刚刚离巢不久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her chicks are not long out of the nest themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们需要知道这个陌生的新物体是食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They need to learn that this strange new object is food.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后发现如何打破它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And discover how to break into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.14,0:22:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是用喙 或许是用爪子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe their beak or perhaps a claw.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 虽然这次胜利 更多地依赖运气而非技巧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Success, perhaps more by luck than skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.39,0:22:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对于下一代偷蛋贼来说 这仍然是一堂重要的生存课程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But still a vital lesson for this next generation of egg thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.74,0:22:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在荒地上 凉爽的夜晚很短暂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the badlands, the relief of cooler nights
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.95,0:22:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧接着是炽热的阳光倾泻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is all too soon followed by the return of the intense heat of the sun's rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙子表面的温度能迅速升至摄氏70度以上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The temperature on the surface of the sand can soar to over 160 degrees Fahrenheit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的水分几乎会在瞬间渗透或蒸发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any water here soaks away or evaporates in seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是地球上最干旱的地方之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is one of the driest places on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.74,0:23:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有水 任何动物都无法生存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Without water, no animal can survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.04,0:23:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 这是这些小多智龙的家园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yet this is home to these young Tarchia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.22,0:23:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们是生活在沙漠中的甲龙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are desert-living ankylosaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.69,0:24:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有厚实的甲片和巨大的棒状尾巴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Heavily armored with huge, clubbed tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.65,0:24:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深色“眼罩”保护着多智龙的眼睛 免受刺眼阳光的侵害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dark patches protect the Tarchia's eyes from the glaring sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.79,0:24:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是多智龙独特的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this is the sound
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.17,0:24:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空调系统的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of Tarchia's very own air conditioning system.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.59,0:24:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当空气从身体内排出时 它们的大鼻子能有效地冷却空气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their large nose cools the air as it leaves the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.68,0:24:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次呼吸都能凝结并保存宝贵的水分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}condensing and so conserving valuable water with every breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.98,0:24:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这使得它们在寻找食物的过程中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It allows them to survive long periods without drinking
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.48,0:24:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以长时间不喝水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as they search for a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.49,0:24:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的高温形成了侵蚀风\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The high temperatures here create scouring winds
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.41,0:25:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将岩石切割成奇异的形状\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which carve the rocks into extraordinary shapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.96,0:25:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它们也会吹走地面土壤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But they also strip the ground of soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.47,0:25:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此 一些植物 依然在岩石缝隙间扎根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some plants, however, manage to take root in cracks between the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.19,0:25:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只能吃上一小口 也值得为之竞争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any meager mouthful is worth competing for.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.62,0:25:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每过一分钟 太阳就升得更高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With every minute, the sun climbs higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.71,0:25:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴凉处会消失殆尽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon, all shade will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.09,0:25:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使作为沙漠之主的多智龙 有时也渴望能喝上一口水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And even these masters of the desert welcome a drink sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.98,0:26:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像许多游牧民族一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like many nomads,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.44,0:26:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多智龙的脑海中有一幅沙漠地图\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Tarchia have a mental map of the desert
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.19,0:26:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够准确地穿越空旷的地形\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and can travel across empty landscapes with unerring accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.16,0:26:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们记住了那些天然泉水所在的稀有地点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They remember the rare places where there are natural springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.67,0:26:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样的沙漠绿洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Desert oases like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.30,0:26:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对能找到它们的动物来说简直是救命稻草\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A lifesaver for animals that can find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.48,0:26:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倾头龙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prenocephale.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.05,0:27:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿洲周围的气氛常常异常紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tensions often run high around an oasis...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.35,0:27:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 展示力量可以避免一场危险的战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but a display of strength can prevent a dangerous battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.49,0:27:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倾头龙终究不过是一种骚扰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the end, the Prenocephale are little more than annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.83,0:27:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但成年多智龙就是另一回事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But an adult Tarchia is another matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.01,0:28:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是体重几乎是 年幼多智龙两倍的成年龙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Especially one almost twice the youngster's weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.81,0:28:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它挥舞着重达22公斤的棒状尾巴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It wields a club weighing almost 50 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.62,0:28:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打起来 年幼的多智龙无法取胜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If this comes to a fight, the juvenile can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.72,0:28:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但援军正在赶来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But reinforcements are on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.98,0:28:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一对多智龙重聚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The pair are reunited.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.99,0:29:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在成年龙要对付之前两倍的棒状尾巴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now there are twice as many swinging clubs for the adult to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.30,0:29:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它决定也许这里有足够的水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He decides that perhaps there is enough water here
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.09,0:29:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,供大家共享\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for everyone to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.78,0:29:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年幼的多智龙终于得以安心地饮水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The young Tarchia can finally drink in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.75,0:29:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 它们可能无法长时间休憩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But they may not be able to enjoy their rest for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.68,0:30:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒地上天气变化的速度十分惊人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In badlands, conditions can change with astonishing speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.44,0:30:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏季气温的上升引发了宽达数百公里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rising summer temperatures fuel electric storms
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.65,0:30:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪电风暴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}hundreds of miles wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.66,0:30:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在德干 这些季节性风暴 导致风向发生改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here in the Deccan, these seasonal storms cause a shift in the wind direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.54,0:30:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几个月前 雌性伊希斯龙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And around the caldera
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.41,0:30:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这些破火山口附近产蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where the isisaur females laid their eggs months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.59,0:30:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今有毒气体已被风吹散\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the poisonous gases have now blown away,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.26,0:30:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为幼龙宝宝提供了一个 关键的生存机会窗口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}providing a critical window of opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.52,0:31:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙子下 奇特的声音响起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are strange sounds coming from beneath the sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.15,0:31:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伊希斯龙在蛋里呼唤着彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Baby isisaurs are calling to each other from inside their eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.49,0:31:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有助于它们同步孵化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It helps to synchronize their hatching.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.03,0:31:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些幼龙相对较小 身长不到30厘米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The babies are relatively tiny, less than a foot long.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.12,0:32:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里除了妈妈的粪便 没什么可吃的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's nothing to eat except their mothers' dung.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.51,0:32:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意想不到的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Surprisingly,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.76,0:32:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粪便富含营养 在很多其他方面 也对幼龙宝宝至关重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's very nutritious and important to the hatchlings in other ways too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.60,0:32:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它将有益的细菌带入它们的肠道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It introduces healthy bacteria into their guts,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.36,0:32:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时还含有信息素 就像气味一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it also contains pheromones that, like smells,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.61,0:32:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能引导它们找到母亲所在的群体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will enable them to find their mothers' herd.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.33,0:32:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带领它们前往森林的安全之地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It will lead them to the safety of the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.72,0:32:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 这段旅程并非易事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the journey isn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.68,0:33:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管风向的改变对它们有利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The winds may have changed in their favor,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.02,0:33:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些年幼的伊希斯龙仍面临诸多危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but many dangers lie ahead for the young isisaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.20,0:33:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉和冒泡的液体泥浆池\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hot springs and bubbling pools of liquid mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.00,0:33:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是致命的陷阱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A deadly trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.45,0:33:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历经两天的跋涉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After two days of trekking,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.95,0:34:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼龙宝宝们的能量储备几近耗尽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the babies' reserves are running low...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.46,0:34:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而母亲们再次拯救了它们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but their mothers have come to the rescue again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.59,0:34:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小植物已在破裂的熔岩中生根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Small plants have taken root in the cracked lava,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.71,0:34:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由掉落在恐龙母亲粪便中的种子发芽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}sprouting from seeds dropped in the mothers' dung.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.52,0:34:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而新的危险正在逼近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But a new danger is heading their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.15,0:34:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今有毒气体消散 掠食者也随之而来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now the wind has cleared the toxic gases, the door opens for predators.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.78,0:34:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一只胜王龙现身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A rajasaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.88,0:34:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么多恐龙宝宝暴露在外 这也许是一场盛宴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With so many babies out in the open, this could be a feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.07,0:35:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熔岩裂缝成了唯一的藏身之地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cracks in the lava are the only possible hiding place.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.33,0:36:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了更多的胜王龙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More rajasaurs arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.74,0:37:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管危险重重 成百上千的幼龙宝宝 终于成功抵达了森林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Despite the dangers, hundreds of babies succeed in reaching the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.50,0:37:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 它们将一同 躲藏在灌木丛中生活数年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here, they will live together hidden in the undergrowth for several years.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.18,0:37:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至最终长得足够大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until finally
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.51,0:37:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有能力加入母亲们的群体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they are big enough to join their mothers' herds.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.98,0:38:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果幸运的话 它们中的雌性将在未来几年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With luck, the females among them will return to this crater
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.57,0:38:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到这个火山口产下自己的蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in years to come to lay eggs of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.37,0:38:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如许多生活在 这些恶劣环境中的动物一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like many animals that live in such inhospitable places,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.38,0:38:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风险巨大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the risks will be high.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.51,0:38:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 在史前地球的荒地上 同样蕴藏着无数机遇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there are also great opportunities in the badlands of the prehistoric planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.14,0:38:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(揭秘《Prehistoric Planet》)
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.57,0:38:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(恐龙是好父母吗 )
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.82,0:38:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个巨型恐龙的蛋化石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the fossilized egg of a giant dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.82,0:38:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自泰坦巨龙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A titanosaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.99,0:38:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋刚产出时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When freshly laid,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.45,0:38:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重约1.5公斤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it would have weighed around a kilo and a half,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.75,0:38:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外壳厚约2毫米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and its shell is about two millimeters thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.38,0:39:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管蛋很坚硬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}While the eggs certainly were tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.22,0:39:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们仍需要保持安全和温暖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they still needed to be kept safe and warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.64,0:39:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 恐龙是如何照顾它们的蛋呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So how did dinosaurs take care of their eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.27,0:39:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护自己的蛋免受掠食者的侵害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In order to protect their eggs from predators
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.36,0:39:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并保持蛋的温度 恐龙演化出一系列策略\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and to keep their eggs warm, dinosaurs evolved a list of strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.48,0:39:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(首席科学顾问 达伦奈什博士)
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.99,0:39:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一个策略是筑巢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of these strategies was to build a nest
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.70,0:39:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并坐在上面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then to actually sit on top of the nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.66,0:39:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们确信某些恐龙会这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We know for certain dinosaurs did this
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.54,0:39:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们实际上有恐龙坐在巢顶的化石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because we actually have fossils of dinosaurs sat on top of nests.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.04,0:39:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这些巢中发现的蛋里 有与成年恐龙相同种类的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eggs found in these nests contain tiny babies of the same species
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.71,0:39:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼崽宝宝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as the adults,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.13,0:39:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是有些恐龙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}providing the first evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.68,0:39:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会照顾幼崽的第一个证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that some dinosaurs looked after their young.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.48,0:40:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管这样可以保护蛋不受天气侵害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But although this offered protection and shelter from the elements,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.90,0:40:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这种孵化方法也有局限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there was a downside to incubating eggs in this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.28,0:40:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在蛋上并真正照看它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Having to sit on an egg and actually look after it means
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.03,0:40:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意味着要在蛋的整个发育过程中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that you are committed to the care of that egg
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.87,0:40:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持对其进行照顾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the entire duration of their development
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.62,0:40:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到其孵化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}up until the point of hatching.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.37,0:40:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对某些恐龙而言 这是值得的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For some dinosaurs, it was a commitment worth making.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.75,0:40:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其他恐龙 如蜥脚龙 面临着不同的挑战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But others, like sauropods, faced a different challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.05,0:40:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于许多恐龙体重达数吨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's likely that some dinosaurs never sat on their eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.43,0:40:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们可能从未坐在蛋上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After all, many of these animals weighed tons and tons
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.52,0:40:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(自然历史博物馆 保罗巴雷特教授)
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.02,0:40:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以免在孵化前将蛋压碎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and would have crushed them before they had any chance of hatching.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.52,0:40:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么它们又有何解决方案呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what was their solution?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.19,0:40:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些蜥脚龙的蛋被放置在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are some sauropod egg clutches
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.45,0:40:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雌性用后脚挖出的长沟中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where the female excavated a long trench with her back feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.54,0:41:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产完蛋后 雌性会再将沟填满\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She then backfilled the trench once she had laid all the eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.29,0:41:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今仍能看到这种行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This behavior can be seen today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.88,0:41:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龟把蛋埋起来 从而保护它们不受掠食者的侵害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Turtles bury their eggs to protect them from predators,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.72,0:41:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳光温暖的沙子使蛋保持理想温度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the sun-warmed sand keeps them at the ideal temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.39,0:41:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 有些恐龙采用另一种方法保持蛋温\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But some dinosaurs had another trick to keep their eggs warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.06,0:41:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为 某些恐龙群体会故意收集腐烂植被\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We think some dinosaur groups deliberately collected
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.44,0:41:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堆积在巢顶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and piled up rotting vegetation.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.70,0:41:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上在装满蛋的巢上形成了一个肥堆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They basically formed a compost heap on top of their egg-filled nests.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.41,0:41:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澳大利亚的丛林火鸡 使用这种了不起的技巧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bush turkeys in Australia use this remarkable technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.42,0:41:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,植被分解释放出的热量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As the vegetation breaks down,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.33,0:41:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足以让蛋孵化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it releases enough heat to incubate their eggs
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.75,0:41:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七周左右\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for around seven weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.05,0:41:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 2010年的一项发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it was a discovery in 2010
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.51,0:42:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭示了某些恐龙采用了更不同寻常的方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that revealed that some dinosaurs had an even more unusual way
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.52,0:42:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来保持它们的蛋温暖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of keeping their eggs warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.85,0:42:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们利用地球本身的热量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They use heat from the earth itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.48,0:42:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阿根廷的一个特定地点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In one particular site in Argentina
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.32,0:42:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了大量蜥脚龙蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's had lots of sauropod egg discoveries,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.70,0:42:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就靠近一些地热温泉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's right next door to some geothermal springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.28,0:42:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为蜥脚龙利用火山活动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're thinking the sauropods were using that volcanic activity
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.62,0:42:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来帮助蛋保暖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to help keep its eggs warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.62,0:42:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德干地区是另一个相关地点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Another location, the Deccan region of India,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.21,0:42:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是白垩纪晚期 火山活动最为频繁的地区之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}one of the most volcanic areas during the late Cretaceous,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.05,0:42:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地区提供了更多证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}provides more evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.55,0:42:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有很多层熔岩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are many, many layers of lava,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.97,0:42:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在熔岩流之间 我们发现了恐龙蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then in between the lava flows, we find dinosaur eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.44,0:42:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐龙选择在这里筑巢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dinosaurs were coming to this location
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.56,0:42:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是在火山高度活跃的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even when it was highly active volcanically,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.98,0:42:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方也作为筑巢地被使用了数个世纪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}using it as a nesting site for literally centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.16,0:43:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 恐龙采用了多种方法 确保它们的蛋能成功孵化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dinosaurs had many ways to ensure their eggs would hatch...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.29,0:43:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 我们可以确定的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we can be certain of one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.75,0:43:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们的方法非常有效\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their methods worked very effectively,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.26,0:43:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使恐龙能够统治地球超过一亿五千万年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}helping them to rule the world for over 150 million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.41,0:45:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字幕翻译:谭萱

